Our cookies and other tracking technologies help provide additional functionality to the Service and help us analyze Service usage more accurately.
For instance, our Service may set a cookie on your browser that saves your login credentials.
You can set your browser or operating system settings to limit certain tracking or to decline cookies, but by doing so, you may not be able to use certain Service features
title: Blocking first party cookies may limit your ability to use the service
